text: Colm Basquel (born 1996) is a Gaelic footballer who plays for Ballyboden St Enda's and the senior Dublin county team. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Ballyboden St Enda's Gaelic footballers Category:Dublin inter-county Gaelic footballers Category:Sportspeople from Dublin (city)
